  fhir:description [ fhir:v "Clinical decision support rule for cervical cancer screening eligibility, scheduling, and cascade routing. Implements WHO Algorithm 5 (HPV DNA + VIA triage) screening entry point for both general population and women living with HIV (WLHIV). Evaluates patient demographics, HIV status, and screening history to determine eligibility, due status, and the patient's current position in the screening cascade."] ; # 
